trans-unit.source: Describes the direction to move a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup"></xref> control to increase the amount of the <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup"></xref> that is visible.
trans-unit.target: 描述移动的方向<xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup"></xref>控件来增加的量<xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup"></xref>可见。

trans-unit.source: This enumeration is a return value type for a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.CustomPopupPlacementCallback> delegate that is used to define custom placement for a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup>.
trans-unit.target: 此枚举是<xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.CustomPopupPlacementCallback>用于定义自定义放置<xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup>。</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup>的委托</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.CustomPopupPlacementCallback>的返回值类型

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup"></xref> control changes position by moving along the horizontal axis of the screen before moving along the vertical axis.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup"> </xref>控件通过先沿垂直轴移动沿屏幕的水平轴移动来更改位置。

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup"></xref> control changes position according to default <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup"></xref> behavior.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup"> </xref>控件更改位置根据默认<xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup"></xref>行为。

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup"></xref> control changes position by moving along the vertical axis of the screen before moving along the horizontal axis.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Popup"> </xref>控件通过先沿水平轴移动沿屏幕的垂直轴移动来更改位置。
